<br>
Strength while Smithing DIRECTLY affects the chance of SUCCESS on a combine...<br>
<br>
Wisdom/Intelligence while Smithing DIRECTLY affects the chance of SKILL UP on a combine...<br>
<br>
So max str when you want to make that Uber Cultural piece and push up the Wis or Int (whichever is higher) when you are doing combines for skill ups.  A balance of the two is of course ideal but that can be a challenge in itself.  <br>
<br>
Kalgareth Nandorei<br>
Zealot of Marr<br>
Vox Populi<br>
<br>
